{"tid":19420,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"［求救］小毒毒乜都唔知去英國","createTime":"2016-12-02T18:29:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-04T20:08:01.000Z","uid":44909,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"954631d852b031d18804729942f0fb44f6653c40","tid":19420,"uid":44909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:29:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的，買左黎緊4月去英國機票，好威威咁同女朋友講book airbnb，但個啲區係邊都唔勁知...<br />\n<br />\n如果留係倫敦九日去下大路景點的話住咩區好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8332cb8201609ea12171dd33eb0a550a00caad07","tid":19420,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:32:32.000Z","msg":"每日都去睇大笨鐘 跟著就返酒店玩大笨象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f75af0c44526b97d8f14f0d6b10beda7d7008aff","tid":19420,"uid":38145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T18:34:23.000Z","msg":"行下牛津街 買下野咁 行哂都應該要兩日"},{"pid":"8323d550b315fe5b93233db13c55b37f5a34ac19","tid":19420,"uid":44909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T19:18:54.000Z","msg":"小弟目標係去大英博物館睇賊髒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"276df868b2924e90b86fec10dc039ad3bec0fac2","tid":19420,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:14:47.000Z","msg":"zone 1既話Gloucester road, south kensington都唔錯 附近又多museum <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實主要都係睇係想去邊, 想平啲定方便啲"},{"pid":"1154542ba7b4da66c5aa196528ad649e22982c82","tid":19420,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小弟目標係去大英博物館睇賊髒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一定要book語音導覽解說<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔係你會唔知自己做緊乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7e1609e16eb059df7232037c57a4886bab92dcb","tid":19420,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:22:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的，買左黎緊4月去英國機票，好威威咁同女朋友講book airbnb，但個啲區係邊都唔勁知...<br />\n<br />\n如果留係倫敦九日去下大路景點的話住咩區好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去英國淨遊倫敦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"4c3581c11ba1296208d35b6cb39063ea22e807e4","tid":19420,"uid":46020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:23:21.000Z","msg":"睇你玩乜啦<br />\n我上個月london 本身plan3日點知兩日已經玩曬<br />\nD倫敦眼呀大笨鐘呀橋呀西敏寺呀白金漢宮呀一日已經可以去曬<br />\n你九日就去埋london附近啦<br />\nEg巨石陣,劍橋 etc"},{"pid":"79670da1bb643984b70240865d3b8fd695d52428","tid":19420,"uid":46020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:24:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>是咁的，買左黎緊4月去英國機票，好威威咁同女朋友講book airbnb，但個啲區係邊都唔勁知...<br />\n<br />\n如果留係倫敦九日去下大路景點的話住咩區好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去英國淨遊倫敦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上網睇好多遊記d人可以玩八日倫敦我心諗......"},{"pid":"bdcd6be7202f529f396878b4f3a25f32932b5a34","tid":19420,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:30:35.000Z","msg":"9日其實好長 你可以玩到好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大路景點就去影吓<br />\nBig ben<br />\nBuckingham palace/Westminster<br />\nHyde park<br />\nSt James Park<br />\nLondon Eye<br />\nTower Bridge<br />\nSt Paul's Cathedral<br />\n<br />\n博物館黎講倫敦係痴撚線<br />\n歐洲平均入場費$100一個，英國免費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nBritish Museum(個人唔認為好特別）<br />\nImperial War Museum(鍾意一二戰歷史必去）<br />\nNatural History Museum(睇吓恐龍骨果啲，強烈推薦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\nTate Modern(藝術野，未必個個岩但入去感受吓果種香港冇既文藝氣息都好）<br />\nNational Portrait Gallery（反正點都會經過，入去睇吓）<br />\n<br />\n市集<br />\nCamden Town<br />\nBrick Lane<br />\nCovent Garden<br />\n<br />\n購物<br />\nRegent Street/Oxford Street行到你仆街<br />\nHarrods<br />\n<br />\n諗到再加"},{"pid":"56da771381364aed31c6f94c9672b76fccd4eef5","tid":19420,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:35:12.000Z","msg":"9日我斷估你唔會淨去倫敦啦（5日頂盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你係博物館迷一個睇5個鐘（我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n咁就去吓<br />\nOxford<br />\nCambridge<br />\nHarry Potter Studios<br />\nYork(古城feel, 鍾意中世紀野可以一試）<br />\nStonehenge/Bath (通常一齊去）"},{"pid":"73fde3c4c992863731c8e04a25fe1c676e4a2ae8","tid":19420,"uid":27766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:36:30.000Z","msg":"你不如講吓你睇咗邊區"},{"pid":"480eb92591d71076016fc8e8908d1d8d511d8f70","tid":19420,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:52:12.000Z","msg":"london 9日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> have fun<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"430e5cb82679ab4e2bad573abbb6d17ade3a9b18","tid":19420,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T21:57:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9日我斷估你唔會淨去倫敦啦（5日頂盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你係博物館迷一個睇5個鐘（我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n咁就去吓<br />\nOxford<br />\nCambridge<br />\nHarry Potter Studios<br />\nYork(古城feel, 鍾意中世紀野可以一試）<br />\nStonehenge/Bath (通常一齊去）</blockquote><br />\nYork遠左啲喎<br />\nLondon附近可以去埋brighton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"acfdafdb371488f95ff199a6e1d94b88e73246ad","tid":19420,"uid":44909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:13:07.000Z","msg":"謝大大<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大人又話要去利物浦探親戚，等我逐樣睇下<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c4714bb86696a14149cdf4aeb4a5a63c3dca386","tid":19420,"uid":7225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T09:58:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>9日我斷估你唔會淨去倫敦啦（5日頂盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你係博物館迷一個睇5個鐘（我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n咁就去吓<br />\nOxford<br />\nCambridge<br />\nHarry Potter Studios<br />\nYork(古城feel, 鍾意中世紀野可以一試）<br />\nStonehenge/Bath (通常一齊去）</blockquote><br />\nYork遠左啲喎<br />\nLondon附近可以去埋brighton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYork唔遠啦兩個鐘火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無同佢講Edinburgh 咪算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb7a4490beb539c0e976152bb672f23276d15c2c","tid":19420,"uid":12185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-03T18:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>9日我斷估你唔會淨去倫敦啦（5日頂盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非你係博物館迷一個睇5個鐘（我試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n咁就去吓<br />\nOxford<br />\nCambridge<br />\nHarry Potter Studios<br />\nYork(古城feel, 鍾意中世紀野可以一試）<br />\nStonehenge/Bath (通常一齊去）</blockquote><br />\nYork遠左啲喎<br />\nLondon附近可以去埋brighton<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nYork唔遠啦兩個鐘火車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無同佢講Edinburgh 咪算係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢都去得liverpool<br />\nYork都ok啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e470890b7501b50ee806c9b952224761d74d21a4","tid":19420,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-04T20:08:01.000Z","msg":"去倫敦千祈唔好貪平或者貪得意搭巴士，如果唔係塞車塞到你番香港嗰日都未到站<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nTfl 屌你老母呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}